On the feast to wait for him the humble to which this Cardinal arrived from the "end of the world" always had an extra look, the attention to the last exalted by the Gospel: "Blessed are the last because they will be the first in the kingdom of heaven." A priest ascended to the threshold of Peter who had never forgotten to be the son of migrants. And so after the esequies reserved to the powerful of the earth, the embrace of a <a href="https://www.agi.it/cronaca/news/2025-04-23/lucia-ercoli- interview-medicina-solidale-il-papapa-dei-poveri-31059634/"> group of poor, migrants, transgender and detaine; That same basilica where Francis used to stop on the return of his journey, even the last: that after 38 days at the Policlinico Gemelli > where he was admitted for a polymicrobiotic pneumonia. With an out-of-program, the procession arrived in the Vatican, resumed the march towards Santa Maria Maggiore where without even getting off the car, Bergoglio entrusted a bouquet of yellow flowers to the archpriest to honor the&nbsp;<em>Salus Populi Romani.</em>
For the burial, as this pontificate was, a <a href="https://www.agi.it/cronaca/news/2025-04-24/papapa-francesco-santa-maria-maggiore-lavori-per-preparare-tomba-31073874/"> semplice in Ligurian marble with the word "Franciscus"/a &nbsp;
